{
  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-160000bcee79",
  "content": "### Task 5: Add CUDA awareness to rebuild command\n\n### Task 6: Update init_flags default and post-create help text\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `.devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh`\n- Modify: `.devcontainer/scripts/post-create.sh`\n\nBoth files are in: `/root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace/`\n\n**Step 1: Add `cuda=disabled` to the default flags**\n\nIn `corvia-workspace.sh`, update `init_flags()` to include cuda:\n\n```bash\ninit_flags() {\n    if [ ! -f \"$FLAGS_FILE\" ]; then\n        cat > \"$FLAGS_FILE\" <<'EOF'\nollama=disabled\nsurrealdb=disabled\ncuda=disabled\nEOF\n    fi\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Update post-create.sh help text**\n\nIn `post-create.sh`, change the final echo block from:\n\n```bash\necho \"=== Post-Create Complete ===\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace status' to see available services.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace enable ollama' for Ollama embeddings.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace enable surrealdb' for SurrealDB FullStore.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace rebuild' to recompile from local source.\"\n```\n\nTo:\n\n```bash\necho \"=== Post-Create Complete ===\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace status' to see available services.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace enable ollama' for Ollama embeddings.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace enable surrealdb' for SurrealDB FullStore.\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace enable cuda' for GPU-accelerated inference (requires NVIDIA GPU).\"\necho \"Run 'corvia-workspace rebuild' to recompile from local source.\"\n```\n\n**Step 3: Verify both scripts parse correctly**\n\nRun: `bash -n /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace/.devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh && bash -n /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace/.devcontainer/scripts/post-create.sh`\nExpected: no output (success)\n\n**Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ncd /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace\ngit add .devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh .devcontainer/scripts/post-create.sh\ngit commit -m \"feat: add cuda to default flags and post-create help text\"\n```\n\n---\n",
